data.name: Delusion Trap Hole
data.desc: If your opponent Special Summoned a monster this turn: Target 1 monster they control with 2000 or more ATK; destroy it, then, if you have a "Hole" Normal Trap in your GY, you can banish 1 monster from your opponent's GY. You can only activate 1 "Delusion Trap Hole" per turn.
